The paper deals with a mechanism for group decision-making, which is a topic studied in game theory (cs.GT), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and data structures (cs.DS). The use of randomized rounding is also of interest to the fields of statistical inference (cs.SI) and machine learning (cs.LG).
